<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Web3 & Blockchain</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-white font-sans">
  <header class="bg-gray-800 p-4 shadow-lg">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Web3 & Blockchain</h1>
      <nav>
        <ul class="flex space-x-4">
          <li><a href="#about" class="hover:text-teal-400">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="#benefits" class="hover:text-teal-400">Benefits</a></li>
          <li><a href="#usecases" class="hover:text-teal-400">Use Cases</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact" class="hover:text-teal-400">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container mx-auto p-6">
    <section id="about" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">What is Web3?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">Web3 represents the next generation of the internet, where users have control over their own data, identity, and transactions through decentralized technologies powered by blockchain.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="benefits" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Benefits of Web3</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300">
        <li>Decentralization and transparency</li>
        <li>Ownership and control of digital identity</li>
        <li>Improved security and trust</li>
        <li>Peer-to-peer interactions without intermediaries</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="usecases" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Real-World Use Cases</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-gray-300">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Decentralized Finance (DeFi)</h3>
          <p>Platforms like Uniswap and Aave allow users to trade, lend, and borrow without traditional banks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">NFTs & Digital Art</h3>
          <p>Creators can mint and sell unique digital assets on platforms like OpenSea and Foundation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">DAOs</h3>
          <p>Decentralized Autonomous Organizations enable collective decision-making and governance without centralized leadership.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Supply Chain Transparency</h3>
          <p>Blockchain provides traceability of products across the supply chain, reducing fraud and inefficiency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
      <form class="space-y-4">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Name" class="w-full p-2 rounded bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 text-white">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" class="w-full p-2 rounded bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 text-white">
        <textarea placeholder="Your message..." class="w-full p-2 rounded bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 text-white"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="bg-teal-500 hover:bg-teal-600 px-4 py-2 rounded text-white font-semibold">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-center p-4">
    <p>&copy; 2025 Web3 World. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
